Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键果然是这第一中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不先把它打下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就无法知道何时会从何方攻来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离目标还有180
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先派2艘快船过去 以夺取中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布旗下的主力则去破坏Requiem本体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.24,0:00:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明ZAFT月球舰队就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想让他们失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定胜负的关键在于速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被敌人的增援包围之前 夺下中继站
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.34,0:01:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离目标还有150
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZAFT军防卫线 现在显示光学图像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长 Archangel以及Eternal正在接近Station One
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而Daedalus也发现奥布舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯卡罗拉西亚级 以及地球军舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva、Gondwana以及月球舰队的半数去Station One
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,余下的去Daedalus的罗兰那里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Station Two怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有舰影接近 数量为2艘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red22 Charlie 距离为120
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题不在于数量和装备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传令进入红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防卫部队立即出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝 出击 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor启动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员进入第一战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去Eternal前面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried、Valiant启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹发射管全部装填Korinthos弹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和 Freedom出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 Justice出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我打开通讯回路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是Eternal的拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向守护中继站的ZAFT军各将士宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在将摧毁那无用的大规模杀伤性武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 是哪个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么非保护不可或是战斗中不可或缺的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是为了和平 还对身着的军装感到骄傲的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让开路来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊雷还有真 你们总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是Logos的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不听议长的劝阻 固执地坚守着自身的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们的残存势力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火 把他们全打下来 为了ZAFT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队司令部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守卫部队正在Station One同Archangel以及Eternal处于交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球舰队以及Minerva立即前去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ar...Archangel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那帮家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没联络也属正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底还是ZAFT军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之给我出动 快让船出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好像没精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是发生了这么多事 而疑惑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实 从Armory 1抢夺事件起到Junius 7的坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及开战后弄成现在这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁都会疑惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过这尽是棘手之事 尽是战火的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该是说「请让它结束了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷 有4枚导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回避 Helldart发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止战斗 请让开路来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西 不管是朝向何方 都不该发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前 Requiem的Station One
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正受到Archangel以及Eternal的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以此攻击了有反抗迹象的联合军Arzachel基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这大概成了他们的藉口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真是让人头痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明不想继续这样战斗下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来 真不知何时才能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但这也是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在万一我们在他们面前有所软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界只会重返混沌与黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边在悲叹一边却在争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争的历史无法终结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当人们在不断探求和平与幸福之时的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界又必将孕育新的Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不想让世界变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才做到这份上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Plan必须得付诸实施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看 真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我已经没什么未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天生染色体端粒过短
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是Clone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了创造出基拉·大和这样一个完美之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被制造了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只是因为「能做到」这一理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但结果 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道造我之人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比常人更早衰老
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经坚持不了多长时间的这身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本无法想像是科学进步的惊人结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一个我诅咒这命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想破坏一切 最后战死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但到底是谁的错 是谁犯了错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们任何人 都是这世界创造的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要结束这一切后回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让我们这样的孩子再次出生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这未来 由你来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我和雷的想法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange 12处 又出现4架M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 Kolintos发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼欧·罗阿诺克 Akatsuki出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢攻击拉克丝小姐的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是吃了豹子胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种是什么M.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先别管这个 该怎么办啊 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出去被秒杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 如果就这点胆量 一开始就别出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鲁蒂尔号在后方支援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别冲到前面 会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为不知道将来会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.99,0:13:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在也只能继续自己坚信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是同感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了将它结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰现在进入战斗状态 Impulse出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部炮管打开 瞄准Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以ZAFT的名义 今天一定要击沉那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库拉提斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 下舵15
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried瞄准 Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么办啊 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想揍的只有那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然又在那种地方鬼混
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露娜玛莉雅·霍克 核心战机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Station One不久就会沦陷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是划得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 他们应该会直接来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说数量也太少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impluse 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧 这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳? 在Eternal吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要战斗 为什么要战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁才是真正的拉克丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然Minerva和守卫部队会消耗他们不少战力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要知道他们很强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不进攻一切就都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马兹 艾尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那招 听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他们还没解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回转30度 Tannhuser启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva 阳电子炮处于发射状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果本舰移动 那Eternal就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你击沉Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛琉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再去其它地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束后一起回去吧 玛琉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 又在这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么干嘛 难道不是要击落那东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要说的不是这事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种事 已经无所谓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是先做要紧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提亚哥 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要击落那东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是真夕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真夕现在不能接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍休息过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们差不多该出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情况…Minerva呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然Minerva也在奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但Station One还是被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在追击朝这里攻来的Archangel他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva 发射氘光束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就这样过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 露娜玛莉雅没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要对她有信心 她很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们将同去Daedalus的主力舰队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破坏Requiem
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并向世人展示奥布的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 世界又会分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要亲手拯救那个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标距离8000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohengrin瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.76,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Messiah现在进入战斗状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部攻击准备启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neo-Genesis 准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange186 出现前进中的巨大物体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要塞?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标 距射程还有20
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反中子干扰器启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各原子核 到达裂变位置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到高能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.36,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标进入射程内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大出力 回避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点重新补充能量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Legend出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny Legend出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷·查·巴勒路 Legend出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真·飞鸟 Destiny出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没想到他竟然还有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva从后方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离22
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 这次就让你彻底消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 上吧 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你的存在 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也许是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为失去的时间已经回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但今天世界也孕育了新的生命 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把握了今天的人真正面对的应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.18,0:23:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士 Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信未来 飞吧 Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:36.53,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,握った拳の強さで砕けた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:47.13,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,願いに血を流す掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:57.18,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,果てない翼と鎖は良く似て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:08.30,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,重さで何処にも行けずに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:17.60,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,亡くすばかりの幼い瞳で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:28.12,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,人は還らぬ星を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:38.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,掲げたそれぞれの火を 命と咲かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:43.83,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,運んで行くことが運命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:58.44,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,輝き刻む 誰もが優しい 刻の傷痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:36.53,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,紧握的双拳粉碎了梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:47.13,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,鲜血染红了双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:57.18,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的双翼如同枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:08.30,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,沉重得去飞不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:17.60,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡充满了幼小的眼瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:28.12,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,星星承载着失去的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:38.06,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,让生命 像纷纷燃起的火焰般绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:43.83,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,命运的转动不会停息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:58.44,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,把人们温柔的光辉 化作时间的伤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:06.26,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の姿は僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:15.68,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,静かに泣いてるよに胸に響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.12,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,何も知らないほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.87,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,幸せというけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:37.96,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はきっと滿足しないはずだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:44.17,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕が選んだ今を生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:47.72,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:55.27,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,君の速さは僕に似ている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:58.98,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,齒止めのきかなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.67,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,空が怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:10.42,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕はいつまで頑張ればいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:20.33,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,二人ならば終わらせることができる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------EDCN-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:06.26,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:15.68,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,犹如静静的哭泣在心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:27.12,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:30.87,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:37.96,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我却无法满足于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:44.17,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,接受自己选择的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:47.72,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:55.27,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,你的速度与我有几分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:58.98,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,当一切无法停止时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.98,0:23:02.67,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,开始害怕天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:10.42,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,我要奋斗到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:20.33,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的话就会让它结束

